snippet.title: Cloudtrail Islands Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
In Cloudtrail Islands, you take the role as Wendy, a newcomer to rural Cloudtrail County.
Using your unique skills with a glider, soar between the floating islands in the sky, collecting items and befriending the locals as you settle down and become part of the community.

Out Now!

Download and play the Full Game now!
Itch: https://cloudtrailgame.itch.io/cloudtrail-islands
Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/Cloudtrail-Islands/403774
